'Losing the Battle of Ideas': Kirk Says the Left Is Resorting to 'Mob Tactics' With GOP Harassment|http://insider.foxnews.com|http://insider.foxnews.com/2018/10/21/charlie-kirk-says-left-resorting-mob-tactics-gop-harassment|Charlie Kirk,Judge Jeanine,Mitch McConnell,Ted Cruz|2018-10-21|||Turning Point USA founder Charlie Kirk said Sunday on Fox & Friends that the left is resorting to &quot;mob tactics&quot; with their harassment of Republican officials.

On Friday, Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell was confronted at a restaurant by a small group of diners.

Thought many others in the Louisville, Kentucky, eatery told the group to leave McConnell alone, it marks the latest confrontation of a GOP official.

Kirk said on Sunday that strategy is a growing trend and that those on the left &quot;are losing the battle of ideas.&quot;

