Kirk noted the defacing of the New York City GOP headquarters and the harassment of Sen. Ted Cruz (R-Texas) at a Washington, D.C. restaurant as more recent examples of the left&#39;s tactics.

&quot;The Democrat mob know they&#39;re losing, but this is a harbinger of things to come if we give power back to the Democrats.&quot;

He added that the result of a potential takeover of the House by Democrats in November would be &quot;bedlam.&quot;

&quot;This is what the left does. They intimidate, the demagogue, they smear and they lie [about] political opponents.&quot;

